{"tid":305673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【男人的困惑】尿兜咁樣樣 網民齊拗應該企邊度至啱","createTime":"2017-07-02T01:17:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-02T05:15:52.000Z","uid":66260,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d1602c34d07ae148e7af1f7d27dae2954a5cd0b2","tid":305673,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T01:17:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170701&amp;guid=56896966&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170701%26guid%3D56896966%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&d=igyKj1mmDXb1OBnzLp32mbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=fa330fd6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170701%26guid%3D56896966%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&h=b02e9fba\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170701&amp;guid=56896966&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170630/large/1498813877_9942.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170630%2Flarge%2F1498813877_9942.jpg&h=5fa4e923&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n澳洲公廁的一個尿兜，考起了來自歐洲的背包客。他發現尿兜裝有一排金屬架，令他很懊惱究竟小便時應該站在金屬格上，還是站在地上。<br />\n<br />\n塔瓦尼安（Aukusti Tahvanianen）在facebook專頁「Australia Backpackers」提出疑問，坦言這問題令他苦苦思索，甚至已失眠了3周，「對我來說，踏在金屬格上較合理，因為就算你高估了（小便）距離，仍可落在尿兜內，但另一方面（金屬架）卻滿是尿液，幫幫我！」<br />\n<br />\n他的疑問引來熱議，不少人也稱有過同樣的困惑，「我也有同樣煩惱，不久前曾在網上問完全一樣的問題，一般共識都是站在架上」、「哈哈，我在這裡住了一年半仍有這疑問，我肯定他們站在（架）上面，但我擔心很多人並非這樣做，換言之我會站在別人的尿液上」。<br />\n<br />\n有網民就稱不用想太多：「站後一點，脫下褲子，靠自己去控制」、「就站在你不會被尿液濺回沾到褲子的地方」。有網民的解釋相對「專業」得多，指尿兜裝設這些金屬架主要是為了小男孩，因為他們「射程不夠遠」，站在架上小便就可避免尿液滴到地上。<br />\n<br />\n塔瓦尼安之所以有此疑問，是因為歐洲公廁的尿兜通常都沒有金屬架。至於香港部份公廁尿兜都有安裝這種金屬架，大家又會如何選擇？<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》"},{"pid":"6cf4abe840b83406f5670da01e27ed9df759015c","tid":305673,"uid":120581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T01:18:16.000Z","msg":"以前中學都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1d2912facf7aba8dbe4994f559b0d7677c71da2","tid":305673,"uid":1790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T01:20:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前中學都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大把學校係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1176f5b3c63807526117aee9ea20a81fae25517","tid":305673,"uid":54929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T01:21:24.000Z","msg":"我都咁諗過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3abcf00dd704ef876e0f9dcf885be4827deaa3a2","tid":305673,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T01:45:10.000Z","msg":"個設計係畀你企鐵架上面嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過通常我唔會企上鐵架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e98bb3a412dde80ab7fb4a4554d2a7ac45450720","tid":305673,"uid":16414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T01:46:46.000Z","msg":"其實呢種要黎做公廁尿兜最好<br />\n成日有水沖住冇咁臭"},{"pid":"5acbae82cbdfaf6aa42c7cdf8a9919233efc5b5e","tid":305673,"uid":120581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T01:48:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>以前中學都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大把學校係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你應該睇得出我入開唔係男廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6f5bb135aa6c37f32a6e083d7a9e3523afcf38e","tid":305673,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T02:01:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/02/100120_558ed3d0d59600229a436